9da7207a-9b98-407a-aae0-4438a0f99844.title: Ogre guard
9da7207a-9b98-407a-aae0-4438a0f99844.text:
I's is guardin' da coffins-ies- make sure no fieves nick
stuff from 'em. If dey's do, dey get's bashed and
shoved down da big 'ole and get deaded by da zogries
in da deadies place. So yous creature be wares...ok!

39d75ecc-8602-4731-9498-8929dce55bee.text:
Da Zogries comes from da deadies place - deys
attacking all da jig-dancers wot do da god stuff... jiggin
an all. Dem zogries gonna dead all on us wiv da sickies.

5f868aed-c08a-4f27-8884-de11853f2e47.text:
We's grabbed da closes dead-uns to stop da zogries
gettin' em..de'se dead-uns coffins got da old-uns boneses
and older-stuff in 'em, Grish seys we's needs to guard
'em...I's does what Grish seys.
